Shopmate Sunday! More than a brother, less than a wife @krakenzglass has been working next to me for over four years now. Theres no substitute for putting in the work and @krakenzglass is the example of that. Coming up through the ranks super fast he quickly found his owns style and has been refining it since.  There maybe a 12 year gap in our age but @krakenzglass has helped me keep my finger on the pulse and keeps me motivated in our shop to say the least.  I'm inspired by his hustle and his overall passion for this medium.  Go check out his page.  Throw him some love.  Give a follow. Pretty sure you can catch him at @eastcoastmelt in September too.  Thanks for looking. @krakenzglass @krakenzglass @krakenzglass
